text: IFK Vänersborg is a sports club in Vänersborg, Sweden. The club was established in 1903, and is most famous for its men's bandy successes. The club has played several seasons in the Swedish top division. During the 2014 World Cup the team played the final, losing 1-4 against Västerås SK. == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1903 establishments in Sweden Category:Bandy clubs in Sweden Category:Vänersborg
